videos.description: Ole Miss players stand for the national anthem after kneeling last week in response to a confederate march on campus.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Ole Miss players stand for national anthem) 2019/2/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ole Miss players stand for national anthem

videos.description: Terence Davis flies in with a posterizing dunk and sends the Ole Miss crowd into a frenzy.
videos.headline: Davis throws down posterizing dunk, crowd goes crazy

videos.description: Terence Davis throws down an alley-oop, his second highlight slam of the half.
videos.headline: Davis throws down another highlight-reel dunk

videos.description: Breein Tyree cans fast-break 3-pointer late vs Tennessee.
videos.headline: Tyree buries clutch 3

videos.description: Grant Williams hits tough shot to put Tennessee ahead, as the Volunteers prevail after a charge is called. Ole Miss' Kermit Davis throws his jacket in disgust.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Williams hits go-ahead basket, Tennessee wins in controversy) 2019/2/27

videos.headline: Williams hits go-ahead basket, Tennessee wins in controversy
